Update from my side:

o I fixed audio/zynaddsubfx in r331300.
o ports/183623 should fix cad/brlcad.
o graphics/tulip, net-im/libjreen, net-im/telepathy-qt4 and polish/kadu
  fail to build because they use an internal CMake macro whose arguments
  changed in CMake 2.8.12. I have a patch that should be committed with
  CMake 2.8.12 that fixes those ports in
  <http://people.freebsd.org/~rakuco/cmake-2.8.12-fix-ports.diff>.
